00:08:35.490 --> 00:08:40.520
awesome reverse osmosis machine that turns
icebergs into awesome water, we'll send you

00:08:40.520 --> 00:08:44.320
that." I was like, alright, I got my ingredient.
[Laughter]

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:47.580
&gt;&gt;Sam Calagione: From Antarctica. So then
we worked out the shipping issues and, cause

00:08:47.580 --> 00:08:51.850
at first we we're like it's brewed with 100
percent Antarctica water, that's what I wrote

00:08:51.850 --> 00:08:57.000
that night, and by two days later looking
